Kudingeka inguqulo entsha yamasevisi we-Google Play. Izozibuyekeza ngokwayo maduze.

"Vula i-Wi-Fi uphinde uxhumeke kunethiwekhi ukuze usebenzise ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi.
Ungasetha ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi noma ubuyekeze ikheli lakho lesimo esiphuthumayo usebenzisa inethiwekhi yeselula."
Sicela uxhumane nenkampani yakho yenethiwekhi ukuze unike amandla ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi.
Ayikwazi ukubonisa Imigomo Nemibandela yenkampani yenethiwekhi. Zama futhi emuva kwesikhathi.
Asikwazanga ukuthola ikheli olifakile ngoba ikheli lomgwaqo alikwazanga ukutholwa, noma idolobha, isifunda, nekhodi ye-zip kungenzeka ayilungile.
Uma idolobha lakho, isifunda, ne-zip zingalungile thepha ku-%1$s, uma kungenjalo thepha ku-%2$s.
Ayikwazi ukubuyekeza ikheli lamanje lesimo esiphuthumayo ngalesi sikhathi. Sicela uzame futhi emuva kwesikhathi.

OKUBALULEKILE - IKHELI LESIMO ESIPHUTHUMAYO SE-911 LIYADINGEKA" Ukuvula ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi, faka ikheli lase-U.S lapho ofuna ukuthi amasevisi ezimo eziphuthumayo athunyelwe khona uma ushayela u-911. Ungaya kuzilungiselelo uphinde ushintshe leli kheli noma kunini. Kubaluleke kakhulu ukubuyekeza leli kheli noma kunini lapho ushintsha khona indawo yakho."

IZEXWAYISO - IMIKHAWULO YEKHOLI YESIMO ESIPHUTHUMAYO SE-911" Uma ushayela ku-911, tshela u-opharetha ukuthi ukuphi. Ikholi yakho ye-911 izoba nge-Wi-Fi kuphela uma inethiwekhi yeselula ingatholakali. Ikholi ye-911 eyenziwe nge-Wi-Fi ingalibaziseka noma ingaphumeleli; ngokwesibonelo, uma isistimu ye-911 ingaliboni ikheli, ugesi unqamukile, noma ukuxhuma kwakho kwe-Wi-Fi kungasebenzi. Amasevisi esimo esiphuthumayo azothunyelwa ekhelini olinikeze ngenhla, ngakho-ke sicela ulibuyekeze njengoba ushintsha izindawo."
Ikheli elifakiwe alikwazanga ukuqinisekiswa abahlinzeki besevisi yesimo esiphuthumayo.
Ingabe uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukusebenzisa leli kheli kusimo esiphuthumayo?
Idolobha, isifunda, noma ikhodi ye-zip oyifakile kungenzeka ingalungi.
Sicela uhlole ikheli uphinde uzame futhi.

"Ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi kukuvumela ukuthi wenze amakholi usebenzisa i-Wi-Fi lapho inethiwekhi yeselula ingatholakali khona.
Ukuze usethe ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi, kuzomele ufake ikheli lase-US. Leli kheli lizosetshenziswa amasevisi esimo esiphuthumayo endaweni yangakini uma wenza ikholi yesimo esiphuthumayo (E911) nge-Wi-Fi kusukela kule foni ngaphakathi kwase-US.
Sincoma ukuthi ushintshe leli kheli uma wenza amakholi usebenzisa inethiwekhi ye-Wi-Fi ehlukile ukuze ulwazi lwendawo yakho lunembe. Ungashintsha indawo yakho noma kunini ngokuya kumenyu yezilungiselelo zokushaya kwe-Wi-Fi."
Ayikwazi ukwenza kusebenze ukushaya kwe-Wi-Fi. Sicela uzame futhi emuva kwesikhathi.
